lead_paragraph: Indiana Pacers guard Monta Ellis had a few chances to close out the Denver Nuggets on Saturday night. He missed on his first try while regulation ended but put the Pacers over the top in overtime.

headline.print_headline: Ellis Scores 32 Points, Pacers Beat Nuggets 109-105 in OT
